title: Geoff Berner - The Wedding Dance of the Widow Bride
description:
1. Good Luck Now
2. Weep, Bride, Weep
3. Widow Bride
4. Queen Victoria
5. The Fiddler is a Good Woman
6. Traitor Bride
7. Can't Stay Dry
8. Song to Reconcile
9. Would It Kill You?
10. Instrumental Weep, Bride, Weep 

Geoff Berner (early in his musical career known as "Potty Mouth" Berner) is a Canadian singer-songwriter on the accordion originating from Vancouver, British Columbia.
